<p>If you have anything more than one line snark, then I'm all ears. If I missed something, it'd be more worthwhile to point it out (almost assuredly resulting in me removing my downvote) than to snipe at me. Right now, it's improbable biology, but nature is REALLY GOOD at freaky weird stuff that makes little to no sense, and various aspects of this SCP exist in real animals.</p>
